com.github.fge.filesystem.filestore

Class FileStoreBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.FileStore
      • com.github.fge.filesystem.filestore.FileStoreBase

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public abstract class FileStoreBase
extends FileStore
    Base implementation of a FileStore

    Notes:

    • at the moment, there is no support for FileStoreAttributeViews;
    • by default, all size methods return Long.MAX_VALUE; as discussed on nio-dev, this is a reasonable value to return when the file store has no information on the actual size.
    See Also:
    FileStore
